"MailBox" is a class that provides a simple interface for
interacting with an IMAP server.

>>> mb = MailBox('imap.example.com')
>>> mb.login('user@example.com', 'password')
>>> mb.folder.set('INBOX')
>>> mb.folder.current
'INBOX'
>>> mb.search()
[<MailMessages count=0>, <MailMessages count=0>, ...
